26quot%3BHe%20told%20me%20he%20was%20in%20importing%20and%20exporting%2C%26quot%3B%20Phillip%2C%20the%20ex-dancer%2C%20said%20on%20the%20witness%20stand%2C%20giving%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiddy-trial-jury-selection-complete-meet-jurors-sean-combs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECombs%20jury%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20earliest%20firsthand%20account%20of%20what%20happened%20at%20a%20%26quot%3Bfreak%20off%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20elaborate%20performances%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20sex-trafficking%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20say%20that%20over%20the%20course%20of%20two%20decades%2C%20Combs%20coerced%20four%20girlfriends%20into%20participating%20in%20these%20staged%20sex%20shows%2C%20which%20the%20indictment%20describes%20as%20commercial%20sex%20acts%20because%20of%20the%20involvement%20of%20male%20strippers%20or%20escorts.%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22%23fef586%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fmark%3E%3Cbr%3ECombs%20has%20countered%20that%20the%20encounters%20were%20consensual.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20has%20no%20place%20in%20his%20private%20bedroom%2C%26quot%3B%20defense%20lawyer%20Teny%20Geragos%20said%20in%20opening%20statements%20Monday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20witness%20stand%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20Phillip%20told%20rapt%20jurors%20that%20he%20believed%20he%20was%20called%20to%20Manhattan's%20Gramercy%20Park%20Hotel%20that%20first%20night%20in%20order%20to%20perform%20as%20a%20dancer%20for%20a%20bachelorette%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20expecting%20to%20do%20a%20little%20strip%20tease%20and%20that's%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20%26quot%3BCassie%20opened%20the%20door%20and%20asked%20if%20it%20was%20OK%20if%20it%20was%20just%20going%20to%20be%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20jury%2C%20describing%20her%20attire%20as%20red%20lingerie%2C%20red%20high%20heels%2C%20and%20a%20red%20wig.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20said%20her%20husband%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20special%20for%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20Ventura%20told%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhillip%20testified%20Ventura%20told%20him%20his%20assignment%20would%20be%20to%20rub%20baby%20oil%20on%20her%20%E2%80%94%20and%20more%2C%20if%20he%20was%20up%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECombs%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20sat%20in%20the%20corner%20of%20the%20darkened%20room%2C%20wearing%20only%20a%20bathrobe%20and%20the%20bandana%20that%20covered%20his%20face%20from%20the%20nose%20down%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20wasn't%20going%20to%20try%20to%20touch%20me%20or%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Phillip%20said%20Ventura%20told%20him%20of%20Combs.%20%26quot%3BI%20said%20that's%20good%2C%20because%20I%20wasn't%20with%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20room%2C%20Phillip%20said%20he%20saw%20velvet%20couches%20and%20a%20table%20topped%20with%20lit%20candles%2C%20bottles%20of%20baby%20oil%2C%20and%20Astroglide%20lubricant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhillip%20testified%20he%20expected%20to%20be%20paid%20%24200%2C%20and%20that%20he%20recognized%20Combs%20%26quot%3Bas%20soon%20as%20he%20spoke%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20complimented%20the%20room%2C%20the%20hotel%20that%20we%20were%20in%2C%20and%20I%20asked%20him%20what%20he%20did%20for%20a%20living%2C%26quot%3B%20Phillip%20testified.%20That's%20when%20Combs%20said%20his%20job%20was%20in%20imports%20and%20exports%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20ended%20up%20having%20sex%2C%26quot%3B%20Phillip%20told%20jurors%20of%20his%20encounter%20with%20Ventura.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutor%20Maurene%20Comey%20asked%20Phillip%2C%20%26quot%3BBefore%20you%20and%20Ms.%20Ventura%20had%20intercourse%2C%20what%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20did%20you%20rub%20on%20each%20other%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhillip%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BBaby%20oil.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20the%20jury%20that%20during%20the%20encounter%2C%20Combs%20sat%20in%20the%20corner%20and%20masturbated.