2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-revamps-pay-structure-rewards-high-performing-employees-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20going%20back%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-fedex-talent-made-amazon-a-logistics-juggernaut-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFedEx%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20falling%20out%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fups-ship-fewer-amazon-packages-shares-drop-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUPS%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20internal%20document%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftariff-turmoil-amazon-seeks-solutions-trade-policy-chaos-internal-email-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20signed%20a%20new%20partnership%20deal%20with%20FedEx%20in%20late%20February%20to%20handle%20some%20parts%20of%20its%20package%20deliveries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FedEx%20deal%20gives%20Amazon%20%26quot%3Bcost%20favorability%26quot%3B%20compared%20to%20UPS%2C%20the%20document%20said%2C%20indicating%20the%20retail%20giant%20stands%20to%20save%20money%20from%20the%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20doesn't%20specify%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20deal%20or%20which%20Amazon%20packages%20will%20be%20handled%20by%20FedEx.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecuring%20FedEx%20capacity%20is%20our%20primary%20solution%20for%20these%20capacity%20constraints%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20internal%20document%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFedEx%20shares%20popped%20in%20after-hours%20trading%20on%20Monday%2C%20following%20BI's%20exclusive%20reporting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2255a16110-2339-4769-98e7-d1b1de8e8729%5C%22%3EAmazon%20comments%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20to%20BI%2C%20Amazon's%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20the%20new%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20reached%20an%20agreement%20with%20FedEx%20to%20serve%20as%20one%20of%20several%20third-party%20partners%20to%20deliver%20packages%20to%20our%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20an%20email%20statement.%20%26quot%3BFedEx%20joins%20our%20other%20third-party%20partners%20like%20UPS%20and%20the%20USPS%2C%20that%20work%20alongside%20our%20own%20last%20mile%20delivery%20network%20to%20help%20us%20balance%20capacity%20to%20best%20serve%20customers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20company%20regularly%20works%20with%20third-party%20delivery%20partners%20to%20%26quot%3Bbalance%20capacity%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20FedEx%20deal%20is%20not%20meant%20to%20replace%20UPS%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f1f168a-002f-43ef-8c82-ee6bf2a94084%5C%22%3EFedEx%20weighs%20in%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20FedEx%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20the%20company%20remains%20%26quot%3Bfocused%20on%20driving%20profitable%20growth%2C'%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20two%20companies%20have%20been%20discussing%20this%20partnership%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFedEx%20has%20the%20global%20network%2C%20capacity%2C%20and%20expertise%20to%20serve%20the%20shipping%20needs%20of%20thousands%20of%20retailers%20in%20the%20e-commerce%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20FedEx's%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20reached%20a%20mutually%20beneficial%2C%20multi-year%20agreement%20to%20provide%20residential%20delivery%20of%20select%20large%20packages%20for%20Amazon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20deal%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bnet%20positive%26quot%3B%20for%20FedEx's%20average%20system%20yields%2C%20the%20company%20added.%20That's%20an%20industry%20metric%20that%20measures%20the%20efficiency%20and%20profitability%20of%20a%20shipping%20network.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22102548fe-fcfa-4b43-b02c-f74222f941f3%5C%22%3EA%20twist%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20renewed%20alliance%20between%20Amazon%20and%20FedEx%20adds%20a%20notable%20twist%20to%20the%20broader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fups-fedex-amazon-fight-over-fewer-deliveries-packages-e-commerce-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshipping%3C%2Fa%3E%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFedEx%20and%20Amazon%20cut%20ties%20in%202019%20as%20the%20two%20companies%20increasingly%20competed%20in%20the%20logistics%20and%20delivery%20space.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20FedEx%20said%20it%20would%20focus%20on%20other%20e-commerce%20customers%20instead.%20Amazon's%20then-operations%20lead%20Dave%20Clark%20downplayed%20the%20fallout%2C%20writing%20on%20X%20that%20FedEx%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20small%20piece%20of%20our%20network%20and%20vice%20versa.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELogistics%20consulting%20firm%20MWPVL%20estimates%20FedEx%20currently%20handles%20no%20Amazon%20packages%20in%20the%20US.%20(Third-party%20sellers%20on%20Amazon's%20marketplace%20are%20still%20able%20to%20use%20FedEx%20as%20a%20shipping%20option).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FedEx%20deal%20follows%20UPS's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fups-to-cut-20-000-jobs-cost-cutting-efforts-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eannouncement%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20it%20would%20reduce%20its%20shipping%20volume%20for%20Amazon%20packages%20by%20more%20than%20half%20by%20the%20end%20of%202026.%20Despite%20Amazon%20being%20its%20largest%20customer%2C%20the%20company%20cited%20profitability%20concerns%20as%20the%20reason%20for%20slowly%20winding%20down%20the%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20internal%20document%20obtained%20by%20BI%2C%20Amazon's%20Extra%20Large%20delivery%20network%2C%20which%20ships%20bulky%20items%20like%20TVs%20and%20furniture%2C%20expects%20to%20get%20some%20delivery%20support%20from%20FedEx%20through%20this%20new%20deal.%20In%20the%20second%20half%20of%20this%20year%2C%20Amazon's%20Extra%20Large%20delivery%20team%20plans%20to%20%26quot%3Bleverage%20FedEx%20for%20100%25%26quot%3B%20of%20any%20capacity%20risks%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E