d%20to%20the%20point%20where%20fishermen%20themselves%20alert%20SSTCN%20when%20nesting%20turtles%20are%20spotted%20or%20when%20eggs%20are%20found.%20Prem%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20nesting%20season%2C%20if%20fishermen%20find%20a%20turtle%20laying%20eggs%2C%20they%20ensure%20not%20to%20disturb%20her.%20They%20even%20keep%20dogs%20and%20humans%20away%20and%20inform%20SSTCN%20volunteers%20immediately.%E2%80%9D%20In%20cases%20where%20hatchlings%20emerge%20unexpectedly%2C%20fishermen%20cut%20their%20own%20nets%20to%20release%20the%20tiny%20turtles%20into%20the%20sea%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETraditional%20vs.%20trawling%3A%20A%20tale%20of%20two%20fishing%20worlds%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20waters%20have%20two%20starkly%20different%20fishing%20methods%3A%20traditional%2Fartisanal%20fishing%20and%20mechanised%2Ftrawling.%20Traditional%20fishermen%2C%20who%20operate%20within%2013%20nautical%20miles%20of%20shore%2C%20use%20small%20catamarans%20or%20boats%20with%20selective%20gear%20like%20gill%20nets%2C%20which%20rarely%20harm%20turtles.%20Their%20knowledge%20of%20tides%2C%20currents%2C%20and%20breeding%20cycles%20is%20generational%2C%20rooted%20in%20observing%20and%20respecting%20marine%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrem%2C%20who%20has%20grown%20up%20watching%20his%20father%20fish%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CTraditional%20fishermen%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%20very%20far.%20They%20use%20nets%20that%20sit%20like%20curtains%20in%20the%20water%2C%20catching%20specific%20types%20of%20fish.%20They%20know%20which%20areas%20to%20avoid%20during%20turtle%20nesting%20or%20mating%20seasons.%E2%80%9D%20These%20nets%20are%20also%20usually%20hauled%20in%20quick